16
00:00:38,264 --> 00:00:39,963
Betty, how could
the Black Hood know that?

17
00:00:39,964 --> 00:00:41,304
Put it on.

18
00:00:41,534 --> 00:00:43,803
<i>Why are you doing this to me?</i>

19
00:00:43,804 --> 00:00:45,103
<i>To show you that we're the same.</i>

20
00:00:45,104 --> 00:00:48,004
Where is he, Betty?
Where did you take Chic?

21
00:00:48,014 --> 00:00:49,713
Did you kill my brother?

22
00:00:49,714 --> 00:00:50,814
I didn't mean to hurt him.

23
00:00:51,884 --> 00:00:53,214
I'm gonna give you a head start.

24
