Don't you mean Hermione lodge?

35
00:01:30,654 --> 00:01:32,914
Take the flyer, Sir,
in case you change your mind.

36
00:01:32,924 --> 00:01:34,354
Sure.

37
00:01:34,355 --> 00:01:36,854
<i>Most people believed Midge
was murdered by someone else</i>

38
00:01:38,194 --> 00:01:39,593
<i>But not Archie.</i>

39
00:01:39,594 --> 00:01:41,993
<i>He was certain,
beyond a shadow of a doubt,</i>

40
00:01:41,994 --> 00:01:43,394
