43
00:01:49,634 --> 00:01:52,234
<i>And suspected he was much closer.</i>

44
00:01:53,304 --> 00:01:55,004
Penny for your thoughts, hon?

45
00:01:56,674 --> 00:02:00,484
I was thinking that he was a test.

46
00:02:02,014 --> 00:02:03,253
Who was?

47
